{"id":282,"parent_id":277,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":282,"title":"2 Samuel 5","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Sam.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 5"],[".studySummary",["i","All Israel anoints David king—He takes Jerusalem and is blessed of the Lord—He conquers the Philistines."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.1","order":"02.11.005.22626"},["b","1"],"Then came all the tribes of Israel to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"David"],"unto Hebron, and spake, saying, Behold, we",["i","are"],"thy bone and thy flesh."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.2","order":"02.11.005.22627"},["b","2"],"Also in time past, when Saul was king over us, thou wast he that leddest out and broughtest in Israel: and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said to thee, Thou shalt feed my people Israel, and thou shalt be a captain over Israel."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.3","order":"02.11.005.22628"},["b","3"],"So all the elders of Israel came to the king to Hebron; and king David made a league with them in Hebron before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],": and they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"anointed"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"David"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"king"],"over Israel."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.4","order":"02.11.005.22629"},["b","4"],"¶David",["i","was"],"thirty years old when he began to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"reign"],",",["i","and"],"he",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"reigned"],"forty years."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.5","order":"02.11.005.22630"},["b","5"],"In Hebron he reigned over",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"Judah"],"seven years and six months: and in Jerusalem he",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"reigned"],"thirty and three years over all Israel and Judah."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.6","order":"02.11.005.22631"},["b","6"],"¶And the king and his men went to Jerusalem unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"Jebusites"],", the inhabitants of the land: which spake unto David, saying, Except thou take away the blind and the lame, thou shalt not come in hither: thinking, David cannot come in hither."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.7","order":"02.11.005.22632"},["b","7"],"Nevertheless David took the strong hold of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Zion"],": the same",["i","is"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"city of David"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.8","order":"02.11.005.22633"},["b","8"],"And David said on that day, Whosoever getteth up to the gutter, and smiteth the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Jebusites"],", and the lame and the blind,",["i","that are"],"hated of David’s soul,",["i","he shall be chief and captain."],"Wherefore they said, The blind and the lame shall not come into the house."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.9","order":"02.11.005.22634"},["b","9"],"So David dwelt in the fort, and called it the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"city of David"],". And David built round about from",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"Millo"],"and inward."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.10","order":"02.11.005.22635"},["b","10"],"And David went on, and grew great, and the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God of hosts",["i","was"],"with him."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.11","order":"02.11.005.22636"},["b","11"],"¶And",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"Hiram"],"king of Tyre sent messengers to David, and cedar trees, and carpenters, and masons: and they built David an house."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.12","order":"02.11.005.22637"},["b","12"],"And David perceived that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had established him king over Israel, and that he had exalted his kingdom for his people Israel’s sake."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.13","order":"02.11.005.22638"},["b","13"],"¶And David took",["i","him"],"more concubines and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"wives"],"out of Jerusalem, after he was come from Hebron: and there were yet",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"sons"],"and daughters born to David."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.14","order":"02.11.005.22639"},["b","14"],"And these",["i","be"],"the names of those that were born unto him in Jerusalem; Shammua, and Shobab, and Nathan, and Solomon,"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.15","order":"02.11.005.22640"},["b","15"],"Ibhar also, and Elishua, and Nepheg, and Japhia,"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.16","order":"02.11.005.22641"},["b","16"],"And Elishama, and Eliada, and Eliphalet."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.17","order":"02.11.005.22642"},["b","17"],"¶But when the Philistines heard that they had anointed David king over Israel, all the Philistines came up to seek David; and David heard",["i","of it,"],"and went down to the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"hold"],"."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.18","order":"02.11.005.22643"},["b","18"],"The Philistines also came and spread themselves in the valley of Rephaim."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.19","order":"02.11.005.22644"},["b","19"],"And David inquired of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", saying, Shall I go up to the Philistines? wilt thou deliver them into mine hand? And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto David, Go up: for I will doubtless deliver the Philistines into thine hand."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.20","order":"02.11.005.22645"},["b","20"],"And David came to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"Baal-perazim"],", and David smote them there, and said, The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath broken forth upon mine enemies before me, as the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"breach"],"of waters. Therefore he called the name of that place Baal-perazim."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.21","order":"02.11.005.22646"},["b","21"],"And there they left their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"images"],", and David and his men",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"burned them"],"."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.22","order":"02.11.005.22647"},["b","22"],"¶And the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"Philistines"],"came up yet again, and spread themselves in the valley of Rephaim."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.23","order":"02.11.005.22648"},["b","23"],"And when David inquired of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", he said, Thou shalt not go up;",["i","but"],"fetch a compass behind them, and come upon them over against the mulberry trees."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.24","order":"02.11.005.22649"},["b","24"],"And let it be, when thou hearest the sound of a going in the tops of the mulberry trees, that then thou shalt bestir thyself: for then shall the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"go out before thee, to smite the host of the Philistines."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.25","order":"02.11.005.22650"},["b","25"],"And David did so, as the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had commanded him; and smote the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"Philistines"],"from Geba until thou come to Gazer."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.1a","order":"02.11.005.22651"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/11.1.1-9"},"1 Chr. 11:1 (1–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.3a","order":"02.11.005.22653"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/14.8"},"1 Chr. 14:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.3b","order":"02.11.005.22655"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/2.4.3-4"},"2 Sam. 2:4 (3–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/12.23"},"1 Chr. 12:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.3c","order":"02.11.005.22657"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/kings-earthly"},"TG Kings, Earthly"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.4a","order":"02.11.005.22659"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/11.3"},"1 Chr. 11:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.4b","order":"02.11.005.22661"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/8.15"},"2 Sam. 8:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/2.11"},"1 Kgs. 2:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/29.27"},"1 Chr. 29:27"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.5a","order":"02.11.005.22663"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/2.4"},"2 Sam. 2:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.5b","order":"02.11.005.22665"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/2.11"},"2 Sam. 2:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/3.4"},"1 Chr. 3:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.6a","order":"02.11.005.22667"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/15.63"},"Josh. 15:63"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/1.21"},"Judg. 1:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.7a","order":"02.11.005.22669"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zion"},"TG Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.7b","order":"02.11.005.22671"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/2.10"},"1 Kgs. 2:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.8a","order":"02.11.005.22673"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/11.4"},"1 Chr. 11:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.9a","order":"02.11.005.22675"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/11.7"},"1 Chr. 11:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.9b","order":"02.11.005.22677"},["b","9b"],"The Hebrew root word suggests a fill, terrace, or elevation as part of the defense bastion.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/9.15.15,24"},"1 Kgs. 9:15 (15, 24)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/11.27"},"11:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/12.20"},"2 Kgs. 12:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/32.5"},"2 Chr. 32:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.11a","order":"02.11.005.22679"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/5.1"},"1 Kgs. 5:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.13a","order":"02.11.005.22681"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.17.14-17"},"Deut. 17:17 (14–17)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.24.23-24"},"Jacob 2:24 (23–24)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.5.5-7"},"3:5 (5–7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/132.38.38-39"},"D&C 132:38 (38–39)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.13b","order":"02.11.005.22683"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/3.2"},"2 Sam. 3:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.17a","order":"02.11.005.22685"},["b","17a"],["span.small","OR"],"stronghold."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.20a","order":"02.11.005.22687"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/14.11.10-11"},"1 Chr. 14:11 (10–11)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/28.21"},"Isa. 28:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.20b","order":"02.11.005.22689"},["b","20b"],["span.small","OR"],"bursting-forth."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.21a","order":"02.11.005.22691"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/14.12"},"1 Chr. 14:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.21b","order":"02.11.005.22693"},["b","21b"],["span.small","HEB"],"carried them away."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.22a","order":"02.11.005.22695"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/14.13.13-16"},"1 Chr. 14:13 (13–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/5.25a","order":"02.11.005.22697"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/8.12"},"2 Sam. 8:12"],"."]]}
